  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.6.8">
<l>ēviṉār kaliyār nalikaveṉ ṟeṉmē</l>
<l>leṅṅaṇē vāḻumā ṟaivar</l>
<l>kōviṉār ceyyuṅ koṭumaiyai maṭittēṉ</l>
<l>kuṟuṅkuṭi neṭuṅkaṭal vaṇṇā</l>
<l>pāviṉā riṉcol paṉmalar koṇṭuṉ</l>
<l>pātamē paravināṉ paṇinteṉ</l>
<l>nāviṉāl vantuṉ tiruvaṭi yaṭaintēṉ</l>
<l>naimicā raṇiyat tuḷentāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord of misfortune incited [my] five senses against me,</l>
<l rend="indent">saying ‘May he suffer’; how do they [still] exist?</l>
<l>I ended the cruelty that [those] adversaries do,</l>
<l rend="indent">you of Kuruṅkuṭi who is the hue of the vast sea.</l>
<l>Bearing many flowers, praising with verses full of sweet words on my tongue,</l>
<l rend="indent">and bowing at your feet,</l>
<l>Coming [here], I took refuge at your divine feet, my father in Naimiśāraṇyam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
